(14, 1, '2021-06-09 12:50:44', '2021-06-09 10:50:44', '<h1 id=\"title\" class=\"a-size-large a-spacing-none\"><span id=\"productTitle\" class=\"a-size-large product-title-word-break\">USB Headsets with Microphone Noise Cancelling, Call Center Phone and Headset with Volume Control and Mic Mute, Single Ear Lightweight Voip Headset for Call Center Work from Home Skype Zoom</span><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-15\" src=\"https://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/61C00-zuEEL._AC_SL1500_.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1390\" height=\"1307\" /></h1>', 'USB Headsets with Microphone Noise Cancelling,', '<ul>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"a-list-item\">NOISE-CANCELLING BOOM MIC DESIGN: The USB headphones with microphone enables to blockout the background noise and gives you a clearer and natural talk. 330° rotatable microphone to pick up voice well that make both of you have a super smooth communication. Business-grade Wideband USB headset phone headphone provides Digital Signal Processing (DSP) and Anti-acoustic shock circuit protects hearing health.</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"a-list-item\">WIDELY USED This USB cored headphone can be applied for Working from home, Office business conference calls, webinar presentations, Call center soft phone calls, Speech dictation, Online courses, Skype chat, Language learning, PC computer, etc. And avaliable for multi UC platforms(skype for business, lync, zoom, microsoft teams, 3cx, cisco jabber, etc.) and other devices with USB port.</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span class=\"a-list-item\">DURABLE--USB PC headset with stainless headband, quality plastics, superior audio microphone and speaker allow for heavy use in offices, call centers and telemarketing, etc. Reinforced cord is built with Kevlar to withstand demanding environment and is protected against office chair wheels, sharp objects and daily use. Telephone headset with 7.87 foot cable permits you to move around the desk when on the call.</span></li>\r\n 	<li></li>\r\n</ul>', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'usb-headsets-with-microphone-noise-cancelling', '', '', '2021-06-09 17:21:51', '2021-06-09 15:21:51', '', 0, 'https://localhost/wordpress/?post_type=product&#038;p=14', 0, 'product', '', 0),
